title: 12 - Shelby Taylor
itunes:title: 12 - Shelby Taylor
description: It’s the other half of Big Willy Nelson! You may know Shelby Taylor from Bitches Brew, the Brooklyn bar show she created with a couple other badass bitches, but it’s time for you to get to know her just a little bit better! Here’s five words to describe this episode: it is worth shouting about.
